最终双方都很高兴
But both sides end up happy.

1026
01:20:49,880 --> 01:20:51,230
就像双赢
Like a win-win.

1027
01:20:51,320 --> 01:20:53,470
更学术一点
More science-y than that.

1028
01:20:53,560 --> 01:20:56,590
如果你想要更科学的说法 打电话给你爸爸
If you want science, call your father.

1029
01:21:10,960 --> 01:21:12,270
谢谢
Thank you.

1030
