现在什么时间
What time is it?

1034
01:21:35,080 --> 01:21:37,870
现在是你该打开你一直珍藏的美酒的时候
It's time you opened that bottle you've been hiding.

1035
01:21:41,720 --> 01:21:44,230
你是不是有什么突破
You cracked something, didn't you?

1036
01:21:44,320 --> 01:21:45,540
没错 过来
Yeah. Come here.

1037
01:21:47,480 --> 01:21:49,030
看这部分
Take a look at this section.

1038
01:21:49,120 --> 01:21:51,830
他好像在说时间
It seems to be talking about time.

1039
01:21:51,920 --> 01:21:54,480
他们的时间符号随处可见
Their symbol for time is everywhere.

1040
01:21:54,560 --> 01:21:56,070
所以这是什么
So what is this?

1041
01:21:57,480 --> 01:22:00,670
一个超光速飞行公式
